Llama Lords is a gaming clan, we play CSS, WoW, TF2 and more.
Please play on our Gun Game server
83.142.230.77:27015

This is a basic 2 bombsite layout that's been painted in pretty and nice. In my opinion it looks like some sort of playground, but really if I had done it with proper textures it would look like some sort of processing facility or old fashioned mill. 
The layout is fair and fun, allowing the player to quickly change their route and situation. The only real dead end is the sniper tower. The area beyond the walls is out of play. The water wheels are rotating and deliver 1dmg per frame if blocked, however they are almost entirely player clipped. 
Thanks to:
[LL] Chase for the water wheel idea
